      "beat_id": "B04",
      "t_start": 28.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10.0,
      "narration_text": "Inside the barrier, the wavefunction doesn't stop. It decays exponentially: psi falls as e to the minus kappa-d, where d is the gap width and kappa is about one per \u00e5ngstr\u00f6m for typical metal work functions.",
